Class SimilarHtmlPattern

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.github.tomakehurst.wiremock.matching.NamedValueMatcher<String>, com.github.tomakehurst.wiremock.matching.ValueMatcher<String>

    public class SimilarHtmlPattern
extends com.github.tomakehurst.wiremock.matching.StringValuePattern
    Check if the HTML is similar to the expected. The HTML strings are parsed into Documents. Two documents are considered to be "similar" if they contain the same elements and attributes regardless of order.

    See HtmlUtils for more information about "similar" HTML.

    NOTE: WireMock.equalToXml(String) does an identical check.
